  <section>
    <div class="sh">
      <div class="label">§ 05 — The Full Workflow</div>
      <h2>Script to upload, <em>one Saturday.</em></h2>
      <p class="lede">Realistic first-video timeline for a working professional. Videos 2 through 10 will feel awkward. By episode 20, this drops to ~4 hours per video as your template library, voice, and editing muscles mature.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="workflow">

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">00:00 – 00:30<div class="dur">30 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Keyword research + <em>topic validation.</em></h5>
          <p>Find a low-competition Hindi/Hinglish query. Good examples: "Apache Spark Tutorial in Hindi 2026", "PySpark vs Pandas", "Data Engineer kya karta hai". <strong>Check search volume + current top videos</strong> — if top 3 results are 2-year-old English-only, that's a gap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">vidIQ / TubeBuddy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">00:30 – 01:30<div class="dur">60 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Bulleted <em>outline, not full script.</em></h5>
          <p>Structure: <strong>Hook (15s) → Why this matters (45s) → Concept 1 → Concept 2 → Demo → Recap → CTA.</strong> Target 10–12 minutes total — the YouTube mid-roll ad threshold. Write in Hinglish the way you actually talk, not in formal Hindi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">Notes / Notion</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">01:30 – 03:00<div class="dur">90 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Build <em>10–15 slides</em> in Canva.</h5>
          <p>Pick a handwritten/doodle template. Use <strong>Kalam for Hindi text, Architects Daughter or Permanent Marker for English.</strong> Marker blue #2563EB for emphasis. Add doodle arrows, sticky-note stickers from Elements. Chart data goes in Canva's chart tool, not Excel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">Canva Pro</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">03:00 – 04:30<div class="dur">90 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Record <em>scene by scene.</em></h5>
          <p>OBS scene with slide capture + circular face-cam. Record in chunks (hook, each concept, demo, outro) — easier to retake a 90-second chunk than a 12-minute take. <strong>Leave 3 seconds of silence at start/end</strong> of each chunk for clean editing cuts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">OBS Studio</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">04:30 – 06:30<div class="dur">120 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Edit in Descript — <em>text-based magic.</em></h5>
          <p>Import OBS clips. Descript auto-transcribes. Delete awkward pauses and retakes by <strong>deleting words from the transcript.</strong> One-click filler word removal. Studio Sound pass. Review auto-captions (especially Hindi/Hinglish accuracy). Add simple zoom-ins on code moments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">Descript</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">06:30 – 07:00<div class="dur">30 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Thumbnail that <em>screams, not whispers.</em></h5>
          <p>Canva, 1280×720, your face with high-contrast expression, <strong>2–3 bold words maximum</strong>, bright yellow or red background, one small doodle arrow highlighting the key concept. A/B test by asking 3 friends which they'd click first.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">Canva</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-step">
        <div class="time">07:00 – 07:30<div class="dur">30 min</div></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h5>Upload + <em>SEO execution.</em></h5>
          <p>Title formula: <strong>[Hook] | [Keyword] in Hindi 2026</strong>. Description: 2-paragraph summary + chapter timestamps + Drive link to slides (watch-time retention hack). 15 mixed Hindi+English tags. Assign to playlist. Schedule community post for launch day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-used">YouTube Studio</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="wf-totals">
      <div class="tl">
        <h5>First video total time</h5>
        <div class="val">~7.5 hours</div>
        <div class="note">One Saturday, if you stay focused</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl">
        <h5>By episode 20</h5>
        <div class="val">~4 hours</div>
        <div class="note">Templates + muscle memory take over</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

